bites.bite: The largest State of Displacement is BAUCHI with 181 reports followed by ADAMAWA with 172 reports.
The largest LGA is MAIDUGURI M. C. with 15 reports followed by MICHIKA with 14 reports.
The largest Ward is RIBADU with 2 reports followed by MAYO LOPE with 2 reports.
The largest State of Origin of Majority is BORNO with 395 reports followed by ADAMAWA with 165 reports.
The largest LGA of Origin of Majority is KUKAWA with 87 reports followed by MADAGALI with 80 reports.
The largest StateName_Previous_State of Displacement is with 640 reports followed by BORNO with 63 reports.
